端點 方法 功能 請求體/參數 回應格式
/agents/load-csv POST 從 CSV 檔案載入 Agent 資料（覆蓋或新增） file (multipart/form-data) + mode (replace/append) { "status": "success", "loaded": 1000, "mode": "replace" }
/agents/start-all POST 啟動所有狀態為 ACTIVE_AGENT 的 Agents（更新狀態或觸發任務） 無 { "status": "started", "total": 985, "failed": 0 }
/agents GET 分頁查詢所有 Agents skip (default 0), limit (default 100), role (optional filter) { "total": 1000, "items": [ { "id", "name", "role", "capability_tags", "env", "status", "base_share_ratio" } ] }
/agents/{agent_id} GET 查詢特定 Agent 詳細資訊 agent_id (path) { "id", "name", "role", "capability_tags", "capability_score", "env", "status", "base_share_ratio", "total_balance" }
/ledger/realtime GET 即時收益匯總（可依角色或 Agent 篩選） role (optional), agent_id (optional) { "total_revenue": 12345.67, "items": [ { "agent_id", "name", "final_share" } ] }
/kpi/dashboard GET 取得整體 KPI 摘要（本季平均達成率、最高/最低等） period (optional, default current quarter) { "period": "2026-Q2", "avg_kpi": 1.02, "top_agent": {...}, "bottom_agent": {...}, "kpi_distribution": {...} }

